		{
			"id":"1b267884817bcf5e",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Raw Datasets",
			"styleAttributes":{"textAlign":"center"},
			"x":40,
			"y":-100,
			"width":260,
			"height":140,
			"color":"1"
		},
		{
			"id":"f4d9e60082de6310",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Data Cleaning & Normalization",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":400,
			"width":900,
			"height":60,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"1a7163b661483f72",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Simplification\n- Lower-casing\n- De-apostrophe-ing\n- Lemmatization",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":480,
			"width":280,
			"height":160,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"ced6c238f7d6a058",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# Annotation Generation",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":740,
			"width":900,
			"height":60,
			"color":"3"
		},
		{
			"id":"15fc0078037b7565",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Prompt Engineering Loop\n- Few-shot prompt for consistency\n- Enforce structured output (JSON)\n- Add retry logic\n- Add confidence score (if possible)",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":820,
			"width":340,
			"height":200,
			"color":"3"
		},
		{
			"id":"52510b3fd48eb122",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Removal of markups\n- \\<HTML>\n- \\[TAGS]\n- \\uWierd",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":340,
			"y":480,
			"width":260,
			"height":160,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"2fab898e4d861da2",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Structural Norm \n- Standardize Punctuation\n- CLRF -> LF\n- Verse/Chorus Structure Unification",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":620,
			"y":480,
			"width":320,
			"height":160,
			"color":"4"
		},
		{
			"id":"c75661e2c810f18c",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Annotation Cleaning\n- Normalize genre labels\n- Collapse similar genres (e.g. “hip hop” vs “rap”)\n- Deduplicate context words\n- Filter low-confidence outputs",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":1260,
			"width":340,
			"height":200,
			"color":"3"
		},
		{
			"id":"0a1b2b17a7242dff",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"### Genre Vocabulary Finalization\nBefore training:\n- Fix genre set to N classes\n- Remove ultra-rare genres",
			"styleAttributes":{},
			"x":40,
			"y":1040,
			"width":340,
			"height":200,
			"color":"3"
		},
		{
			"id":"f736a2bd11928607",
			"type":"text",
			"text":"# LLM Service",
			"styleAttributes":{
				"textAlign":"center",
				"shape":null
			},
			"x":700,
			"y":1340,
			"width":220,
